        "rationale": "That's the arc length, not the sector area."
      },
      {
        "id": "D",
        "text": "12π",
        "rationale": "Correct."
      }
    ],
    "correct_choice": "D",
    "explanation": "Sector area = (θ/360)·πr² = (120/360)·π·6² = 12π.",
